elements.name: As a user I want to delete tag

steps.name: I enter "l.solier@uniandes.edu.co" into input field having name attribute "identification"
I enter "Lui$$olier15" into input field having name attribute "password"
I click on element having css selector "button.login"
I click on element having xpath "//a[@href='#/tags/']"
I click on element number "0" having css selector "li.gh-tags-list-item" of list having css selector "ol.tags-list"
I click on element having xpath "//button[span/text()='Delete tag']"
I click on element having xpath "//button[span/text()='Delete']"
